description:
Great British Menu - Series 10, Episodes 6 to 10




SouthWest

Three of the south west's finest chefs - Jude Kereama, Josh Eggleton and Dominic Chapman - attempt to impress a veteran judge with their starters. As the only newcomer in the kitchen, Jude is determined to plate up a winning dishes, but he faces stiff competition in the two returnees.




Original Air Dates: 10-Aug-2015 to 14-Aug-2015
